OL,3,CRed Bull boss Christian Horner faces
OL,4,Chearing after claims about behaviour
OL,6,FRed Bull boss will face a hearing on
OL,7,FFriday as he prepares to defend
OL,8,Fhimself against an accusation of
OL,9,F"inappropriate behaviour".
OL,11,FThe 50-year-old team principal
OL,12,F"completely denies" the claims which
OL,13,Fwere made by another member of staff
OL,14,Fat the British-based team.
OL,16,FRed Bull, the Austrian energy drinks
OL,17,Fcompany which owns the Milton Keynes-
OL,18,Fbased team, confirmed on Monday an
OL,19,Findependent investigation had been
OL,20,Flaunched after it was made aware of
OL,21,Fthe allegations.
