OL,4,Chearing after claims about behaviour
OL,6,FIt is not clear where the hearing will
OL,7,Fbe held, while a conclusion is not
OL,8,Fexpected on the day.
OL,10,F"After being made aware of certain
OL,11,Frecent allegations, the company
OL,12,Flaunched an independent
OL,13,Finvestigation," a spokesperson for Red
OL,14,FBull said.
OL,16,F"This process, which is already under
OL,17,Fway, is being carried out by an
OL,18,Fexternal specialist barrister.
