OL,3,CRed Bull boss Christian Horner faces
OL,4,Chearing after claims about behaviour
OL,6,F"The company takes these matters
OL,7,Fextremely seriously and the
OL,8,Finvestigation will be completed as
OL,9,Fsoon as practically possible. It would
OL,10,Fnot be appropriate to comment further
OL,11,Fat this time."
OL,13,FHorner has been in charge at Red Bull
OL,14,Fsince they entered Formula One 19
OL,15,Fyears ago.
OL,17,FDuring that time he has overseen seven
OL,18,Fdrivers' world championships and six
OL,19,Fconstructors' titles.
