OL,4,Chearing after claims about behaviour
OL,6,FThe team dominated last season,
OL,7,Fwinning 21 of the 22 races in 2023 as
OL,8,FMax Verstappen defended his drivers'
OL,9,Fcrown.
OL,11,FRegardless of the outcome of Friday's
OL,12,Fplanned investigation, it has
OL,13,Fovershadowed the start of the 2024
OL,14,Fcampaign, with Red Bull set to unveil
OL,15,Ftheir new car on February 15 ahead of
OL,16,Fpre-season testing and the opening
OL,17,Frace in Bahrain next month.
